import React from 'react'
import Home from '../PageBody/Home'
import SlideCard from '../PageBody/SlideCard'
import Data from '../PageBody/Data'

const productItems=Data.productItems

const Pages = (productItems) => {
  return (
    <>
        <Home/>
        <SlideCard productItems={productItems} />
    </>
  )
}

export default Pages
